title: Vindicated Ken Paxton blames Biden and Texas House for 'sham impeachment'
description: AUSTIN, Texas — Vindicated Attorney General Ken Paxton lambasted the Biden administration and the Texas House for forcing a "sham impeachment" trial following his acquittal on all 16 counts.

title: Oregon Republicans file for reelection despite possible disqualification
description: A group of Republican lawmakers in Oregon are filing for reelection despite being in possible violation of a state law that could disqualify them from seeking office.
